headline: 3 Reasons to Sell WYNN and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Wynn Resorts’s shares (currently trading at $83.10) have posted a disappointing 18.6% loss while the S&P 500 was down 1.7%. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
